column5: <object width="450" height="370"><param name="movie" value="http://www.liveleak.com/e/233_1232912190"></param><param'>http://www.liveleak.com/e/233_1232912190"></param><param name="wmode" value="transparent"></param><embed src="http://www.liveleak.com/e/233_1232912190" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" wmode="transparent" width="450" height="370"></embed></object>   Puffer fish, pretty cool video.
I caught a couple of spineless puffers in flordia, weird fish. After I let them go they would float around for a bit like a beachball.

Cool stuff, I caught a few pufferfish in myrtle beach right off the dock when I was a kid on vacation with my family.  Some would come up puffed out, others not, but they all had the spikes.  I don't remember how we released them as I was only 7 or 8 years old.
They sure seem to like that sommersault thing.
This guy hangs in the entrance to my livingroom.

My uncle has one on his TV.LOL  One of my friends had a saltwater aquarium and had a boxfish in his tank.  He tried playing with it just like in the video clip and it ended up poisoning everything in the tank.
